C. Trigonometry
Basic Identities: 468. sin²θ + cos²θ = 1 469. tan²θ + 1 = sec²θ 470. 1 + cot²θ = csc²θ 471. tan θ = sin θ/cos θ 472. cot θ = cos θ/sin θ = 1/tan θ 473. sec θ = 1/cos θ 474. csc θ = 1/sin θ

