D. Vectors
Basic Operations: 518. Vector addition: a + b = (a₁+b₁, a₂+b₂, a₃+b₃) 519. Scalar multiplication: ka = (ka₁, ka₂, ka₃) 520. Magnitude: |a| = √(a₁² + a₂² + a₃²) 521. Unit vector: â = a/|a| 522. Zero vector: 0 = (0,0,0) 523. Negative: -a = (-a₁, -a₂, -a₃)

