Basic Rules: 585. Power rule: d/dx(xⁿ) = nxⁿ⁻¹ 586. Constant: d/dx(c) = 0 587. Constant multiple: d/dx(cf) = c·df/dx 588. Sum rule: d/dx(f+g) = df/dx + dg/dx 589. Product rule: d/dx(fg) = f'g + fg' 590. Quotient rule: d/dx(f/g) = (f'g - fg')/g² 591. Chain rule: d/dx[f(g(x))] = f'(g(x))·g'(x)

